{"tid":1428783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警香蕉糖惡行開始於秋葉原被公審","createTime":"2019-08-07T11:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T11:21:54.000Z","uid":276385,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9dba748ded05155be0d57cb2a039e3e4d48c035d","tid":1428783,"uid":276385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:00:06.000Z","msg":"食屎啦香蕉糖 夠薑搵我隻揪呀<br />\n你老母雷射筆都可以話係武器<br />\n證物嚟㗎 拆咗件證物出去記者會公審<br />\n同捏造證據有咩分別？<br />\n我點知你開記者會之前對支筆有冇郁過手腳㗎<br />\n<br />\n你哋咁鍾意公審人 即刻係秋葉原皇天擊殺香蕉糖<br />\n死黑警 你地濫用權力迫害香港人 反社會 <br />\n全世界都睇到你地有幾賤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZBGfNFq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZBGfNFq.png&h=b15557b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/185944_089b009a28469603965e8e85d6dbd0e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F185944_089b009a28469603965e8e85d6dbd0e5.png&h=2d9721e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f6c0f894e472b2f9ce8e174e40eb6ab0d746142","tid":1428783,"uid":276385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:20:11.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"c522c5bd8c492702d28b4f8de17fae02f7f6d348","tid":1428783,"uid":243407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:21:54.000Z","msg":"唔好破壞人地嗰環境啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}